    CROMOSIM is a python package which contains the programs used in the
    book "Crowds in Equations: An Introduction to the Microscopic Modeling
    of Crowds", Advanced Textbooks In Mathematics, World Scientific Europe
    Ltd (oct. 2018) written by S. Faure and B. Maury.

